article_summary:
Last week, I thought McCarthy took some of the flexibility out of the offense and just made Rodgers run his plays.
They know he's capable of changing plays at any time, so they try to wait until there's no time left on the clock.
They try to wait until the last minute to show it.
I think it worked very well.
